798
01:00:12,042 --> 01:00:13,335
<b>dan sedih.</b>

799
01:00:16,129 --> 01:00:18,757
<b>Terus tinggal bersama kami di rumah kami</b>

800
01:00:20,300 --> 01:00:21,885
<b>semasa awak berada di Bandar Seongjin.</b>

801
01:00:26,682 --> 01:00:29,351
<b>Ibu saya sangat sukakan awak.</b>

802
01:00:29,434 --> 01:00:30,268
<b>Dan...</b>

803
01:00:32,729 --> 01:00:35,816
<b>Sang-tae suka tinggal bersama kami juga.</b>

804
01:00:41,446 --> 01:00:42,614
<b>Tolong buat itu untuk saya.</b>

805
01:01:08,849 --> 01:01:10,308
<b>O Ji-wang teruk.</b>

806
01:01:10,642 --> 01:01:11,643
<b>O Ji-wang.</b>

807
01:01:12,644 --> 01:01:16,773
<b>O Ji-wang ... O Ji-wang adalah orang jahat.</b>

808
01:01:19,151 --> 01:01:21,653
<b>Dia mungkin doktor, tapi dia orang jahat.</b>

809
01:01:21,737 --> 01:01:25,157
<b>O Ji-wang sungguh pantas. Dia teruk.</b>

810
01:01:25,240 --> 01:01:28,076
<b>Dia... Dia perlu belajar adabnya. 
