<b>Awak mencari abang awak?</b>

829
01:02:42,234 --> 01:02:43,235
<b>Awak ada nampak dia?</b>

830
01:02:43,944 --> 01:02:46,863
<b>Dia pergi bersama Cik Ko.</b>

